abstract: Days after the March 10 crash of a Kenya-bound Ethiopian Airlines’ Boeing jet that killed all 157 people on board, strangers began calling or visiting bereaved families, saying they represented U.S. law firms.

abstract: An unmarried Chinese woman filed a suit against a hospital on Monday for rejecting her request to undergo a medical procedure to freeze her eggs due to her marital status, in China's first legal challenge of a woman fighting for her reproductive rights.

abstract: The fantasy series based on novels by Philip Pullman wraps up its first season. And rivals clash on Monday Night Football.
snippet: The fantasy series based on novels by Philip Pullman wraps up its first season. And rivals clash on Monday Night Football.
lead_paragraph: GREEN BAY PACKERS VS. MINNESOTA VIKINGS 8:15 p.m. on ESPN. The two teams at the top of the N.F.C. North meet in Minneapolis in the final Monday Night Football game of the year. The Minnesota Vikings haven’t lost at home all season and have never lost to the Packers at U.S. Bank Stadium but they trail their regional rivals in the standings. They were also defeated in an earlier matchup at Lambeau Field in September. With the regular season just two games away from completion there’s still plenty to fight for. The Vikings have yet to clinch a playoff spot and the Packers are competing for postseason privileges. Minnesota fans may be hoping that the Vikings’s offensive edge and passionate home support will be enough to avoid a regular season series sweep.

abstract: World stocks hovered near record highs and currency markets were little changed on Monday as trading dwindled before the Christmas holiday and investors looked with confidence toward the new year.

lead_paragraph: MILAN — World stocks hovered near record highs and currency markets were little changed on Monday as trading dwindled before the Christmas holiday and investors looked with confidence toward the new year.

abstract: A kangaroo has been spotted cooling off in backyard pool in a bush fire-ravaged region of Australia while elsewhere firefighters have been rescuing koalas from trees threatened by flames.

lead_paragraph: MELBOURNE/SYDNEY — A kangaroo has been spotted cooling off in backyard pool in a bush fire-ravaged region of Australia while elsewhere firefighters have been rescuing koalas from trees threatened by flames.
headline_main: Exhausted Kangaroo Cools Down in Backyard Pool as Bushfires Rage

abstract: Supermodels and social media mavens, their makeup artists and hair stylists in tow, posed at a concert in leather pants, chunky sweaters and trendy black combat boots. What was unusual about these Instagram posts was that they were all deliberately tagged in Riyadh, Saudi Arabia.

lead_paragraph: DIRIYAH, Saudi Arabia — Supermodels and social media mavens, their makeup artists and hair stylists in tow, posed at a concert in leather pants, chunky sweaters and trendy black combat boots. What was unusual about these Instagram posts was that they were all deliberately tagged in Riyadh, Saudi Arabia.
headline_main: Saudi Arabia Cuts Loose With Bevy of Models and a Rave
